Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}《蓝色星球》第二季{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}南极洲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}地球上最寒冷 最严酷 最遥远的大陆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,0:00:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}从来没有人到过南极洲周围的深海里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}直到现在才有人涉足这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}深海就和太空一样富有挑战性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们对火星地表的了解更甚于{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}对深海的了解{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在我们要潜入这些未经探测的深海{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}发现其中的奥秘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}沿着浮在水中的冰山壁侧面潜入海底{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们来到了一个残酷的世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里的水温是地球上最低的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们在潜入海底的同时 水压也会迅速增加{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}上方的光线只会消失殆尽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}但神奇的是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里竟然有生命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们或许以为极地海洋的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}深海处会是一片荒芜的景象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}但实际上 我们却发现这里的生物异常丰富{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这一富饶的情形并不是只出现在南极洲的海里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}水流会将这份丰饶带往世界各地的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}深海{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}令人吃惊的是 这深海里的生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}竟然比地球其他地方的都要丰富{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:05:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}深海{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}阳光逐渐消失 海里变得越来越暗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}置身于太平洋200米深的水下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们来到了一个陌生的世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}黄昏区{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}深海里永远是一片暗无天日的景象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这儿有着稀奇古怪的生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}火体虫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}身长两米 外形似管 通体呈胶状 从上方来的远洋白鳍鲨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}在对比之下也相形见绌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}只有一点光线能渗透至这个位置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}在这里生存下去便意味着 要充分利用好这点微光{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}剑鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}剑鱼的眼睛和网球差不多大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这有助于它看清楚暗无天日的环境{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}鱿鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过这种鱿鱼只在这里生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的右眼始终看向下方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过左眼要大得多 而且也养成了向上方看的习惯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是为了搜寻水面附近游动的猎物轮廓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}难怪它会被人们戏称为斗鸡眼鱿鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}比这种鱿鱼更稀奇的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}是后肛鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这种鱼的头部是透明的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}里面充满了胶质 它的眼睛能透过脑袋向上方看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们现在知道黄昏区是海洋中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}多达九成鱼类的庇护所{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}只有在夜间 成群的灯笼鱼才会洄游至水面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}寻找微小的浮游生物喂饱肚子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}白天时 它们就回到海底这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}美洲大赤鱿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}身长两米 体重达50千克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}和大多数鱿鱼一样是贪婪的捕食者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里有成百上千只{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们发现南美洲海岸附近{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}有一大群灯笼鱼 就躲在水下800米处{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们的触手上长有强劲有力的吸盘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些吸盘是用来抓猎物的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}如果这里抓不到灯笼鱼了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们就会自相残杀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只美洲大赤鱿用自己的触手抓到了一只小美洲大赤鱿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了把自己的猎物藏起来 不被其他鱿鱼发现{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它会释放出墨液遮掩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过一只更大的美洲大赤鱿跑来挑衅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}还偷走了它的猎物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}黄昏区是美洲大赤鱿最常来的猎区{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们很少潜入{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}底下那暗无天日的深海世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}午夜区{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}阳光无法渗透至水面一千米以下的位置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这漆黑空洞的深海{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}比地球上所有的栖息地加起来都要大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里有生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}只不过不是我们熟悉的那种生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些酷似外星人的生物能释放出耀眼的光线{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}几乎所有的动物都需要吸引配偶 驱逐捕食者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里的动物大量使用光线进行交流{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些信号或许是地球上最为常见的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}交流形式{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是我们却对它们所知甚少{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}捕食者照亮自己是为了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}吸引好奇的猎物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是尖牙鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它牙齿与自身体积的比例是所有鱼类中最大的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}尖牙鱼从头到尾都布满了压力传感器官 能够探测到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}周围水里的任何动静{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它是午夜区最贪婪的鱼类{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}但猎物会利用光亮来干扰对方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些发光的墨液被作为诱饵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}在这漆黑的深海里{\r}
