Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}寻觅和筛选蠕虫{\r}
