Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}在上方高处 一头巨大的{\r}
