Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}六鳃鲨的嗅觉极其敏锐{\r}
