Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.35,0:26:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}抹香鲸的骸骨在四分五裂之际 牙齿也被其他动物{\r}
